<placeName cert="high">Philadelphia</placeName>
<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="psi;4;369" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">PSI4,369;PSI5,pX;PSI6,pXII</xref></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Δωρίων Ζήνωνι χαίρειν. ἐπυθόμεθα ἀφ᾽ οὗ χρόνου κεῖται τὰ διὰ Χάρμου ἐνέχυρα <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ποτη</supplied>-

    <lb n="2"/>ρίδια καὶ κοσμάρια· ἔστιν τὸ κεφάλαιον ἀργυρίου <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμαὶ</ex></expan> <num value="600">χ</num> καὶ τόκος ἑκάστης μνᾶς <expan>ἀ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ργυ</unclear><ex cert="high">ρίου</ex></expan> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost"><expan><ex cert="high">δραχμαὶ</ex></expan> </supplied><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost"><foreign lang="la">.</foreign> ὁ δὲ</supplied> 

    <lb n="3"/>χρόνος ἔτη <num value="2">β</num> καὶ <expan>μῆ<ex cert="high">νες</ex></expan> <num value="11">ια</num>. ὁμοίως δὲ καὶ τὰ <choice><corr>ἕ<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">τε</supplied>ρα</corr><sic>ερα</sic></choice>· τὸ κεφάλαιον <expan>ἀργυ<ex cert="high">ρίου</ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμαὶ</ex></expan> <num value="900">ϡ</num>, ἀφ᾽ ὧν 

    <lb n="4"/>παρὰ Πετάλιος <choice><corr>ἐν</corr><sic>εμ</sic></choice> πόλει <expan>ἀργυ<ex cert="high">ρίου</ex></expan> <supplied cert="high" reason="omitted"><expan><ex cert="high">δραχμαὶ</ex></expan></supplied> <num value="600">χ</num> καὶ <choice><corr>ἐν</corr><sic>εμ</sic></choice> Μέμφει Κάλλωνι <expan>ἀργυ<ex cert="high">ρίου</ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμαὶ</ex></expan> <num value="300">τ</num> <expan><ex cert="high">γίνονται</ex></expan> <expan>ἀργυ<ex cert="high">ρίου</ex></expan> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost"><expan><ex cert="high">δραχμαὶ</ex></expan> <num value="900">ϡ</num></supplied>· 

    <lb n="5"/>ὁ δὲ χρόνος ἐνιαυτὸς καὶ <expan>μῆ<ex cert="high">νες</ex></expan> <num value="5">ε</num>. περὶ δὲ τῶν <num value="900">ϡ</num> <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμῶν</ex></expan> τοῦ τόκου μὴ φρόντιζε, <choice><corr>ἀλ<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">λ᾽</supplied></corr><sic>αλ</sic></choice> ὡς ἄ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν σοι</supplied> 

    <lb n="6"/>φα<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ί</unclear>νηται, οὕτως ποίει. καλῶς δὲ ποιήσεις καὶ παρὰ Σωστράτου <expan>ἀργυ<ex cert="high">ρίου</ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="32">λβ</num> ἃ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ς</unclear> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἔχω</supplied> 

    <lb n="7"/>διὰ τραπέζης ὑπὲρ Διονυσίου φροντίσας ὅπως ἀποσταλῇ μοι. συνέθηκε δὲ <expan><ex cert="high">τάλαντον</ex></expan> <num value="1">α</num> 

    <lb n="8"/>ἀποδόσθαι <choice><corr>ἐν</corr><sic>εμ</sic></choice> Μέμφει, ὃ συνέταξεν δοῦναι εἰς τὰ ὀψώνια Πάιτι καὶ Φαλοῦτι καὶ 

    <lb n="9"/>ἄλλα <expan><ex cert="high">τάλαντα</ex></expan> <num value="2">β</num> <expan><ex cert="high">γίνεται</ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">τάλαντα</ex></expan> <num value="3">γ</num>. ἔγραψε δέ μοι πρὸς Θράσωνα ἐπιστόλιον ὑπολογῆσαι ὧν 

    <lb n="10"/>τὴν τιμὴν οὐθεὶς δέδωκεν. 

    <lb n="11"/>ἔρρωσο. <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="36">λϛ</num> Μεχεὶρ <num value="2">β</num>. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="12"/>Ζήνωνι. 

    <lb n="13"/><expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="36">λϛ</num> Μεχεὶρ <num value="12">ιβ</num>. Δωρίων 

    <lb n="14"/>ποτηριδίων, <expan>Σωστράτ<ex cert="high">ου</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="15"/><expan>ἀ<ex cert="high">ργυρίου</ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="32">λβ</num>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.1862" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.1862" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-249" notBefore="-249" type="textDate" value="-0249-03-24">24. März 249 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.1862" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. J. Cowey .</p></div><div n="meta.1862" part="N" subtype="mentionedDates" type="commentary"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>Z. 13: <date type="mentioned" value="-0249-04-03">3. Apr. 249 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.1862" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Zen. Pestm.</title><biblScope type="numbers">31</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">1862</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0229</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">31</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0229;;31" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.1862" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.1862" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">PSI IV 369</bibl></div><div n="meta.1862" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><geogName cert="high" type="nome">Arsinoites</geogName>, <geogName cert="high" key="Aegyptus" type="ancientRegion">Egypt</geogName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>